{"tid":381140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違逗留條件在囚女子早產　母嬰相繼不治","createTime":"2017-08-30T16:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T07:00:02.000Z","uid":42188,"like":488,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98a9b0121266f72e476712436283ac6b3e9a3bba","tid":381140,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"羅湖懲教所一名42歲懷孕在囚人士，今日（8月30日）在公立醫院早產後不治。該名在囚人士2017年7月20日因管有及使用偽造身份證和違反逗留條件被判入獄，當時懷孕23周。<br />\n<br />\n8月24日，該女子因身體不適被安排入住院所醫院接受治療及觀察。今晨零時38分，她於院所醫院內發現下體出血，經診治後被送往公立醫院接受進一步治療。其後她因懷疑患有妊娠毒血症，而於上午3時40分進行緊急剖腹生產及誕下早產嬰兒。該名嬰兒出生時情況不穩，經搶救後上午4時34分不治。其後該名在囚人士於手術後情況轉差，並於中午12時05分不治。"},{"pid":"6741fc9eac93047e93feae7ba2c69615f90a9225","tid":381140,"uid":6845,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"c2e174ebf21fcf6f7a2e32131ebf2e17ae1e323e","tid":381140,"uid":45788,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"原本諗住幫個b做香港居民呃食<br />\n家陣賠了夫人又折兵<br />\n仲要自己都死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a0c4f68ffd8ea6ba8228fbb8894271e671837b","tid":381140,"uid":4942,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又少兩隻蝗"},{"pid":"82869dab0598e1f18b21f658326eb0b7efd8a963","tid":381140,"uid":42188,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又少兩隻蝗</blockquote><br />\n原文無講係咪蝗<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">雖然應該都係</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cbae4aaf2d5ec8bad3d5e2f0e0a2e6d06be6